description: Kara has been stopping the wrestlers this season. She went up against one of our best, strongest wrestler, Cheyenne Jewel and made her look like an amateur. Kara has been destroying girls on our mats and making really really good wrestlers just look really really bad. Izamar has gone up against Kara in the past and has fallen short each and every time. She believes today she has Kara's number and knows how to take her down. Loser is fisted and humiliated for being such a loser and left crying on the mats, sucking her thumb like a little baby bitch
title: Summer Vengeance Season 11 finals
